- SNS topic
- pub/sub
- one message and many receivers
- One SNS topic subscribed by multiple consumers. Each will get their copy of message.
- Upto 1cr subscriptions per topic
- 1 lakh topic limits
- Subscribers can be: SQS, HTTP/HTTPS, lambda, email, sms, mobile notification
- Data is not persisted(lost if not delivered)

Encryption, Access controls and SNS access policies same as SQS

Note:
SNS cannot send messages to SQS FIFO queues(AWS limitation)